Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.27,slogan,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(214,268)}扔到垃圾箱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起做嘛 模仿海獭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前和家人一起去水族馆的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一回到家 小冠就「海獭 海獭」地说个没完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把橙子放在肚子上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是小时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 晶马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你模仿的海马 也是一绝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海马 海马 海马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 企鹅泳游得好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过在陆地上就有点呆呆的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被晶马这么说 企鹅可会跟你急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我接个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是女孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 我会处理好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我都要被一群「花花公子冠叶菌」给传染了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:50.95,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 企鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要这么大声说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企鹅又不会跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 企鹅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬 我们去买纪念品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只要是阳毬喜欢的 我都可以买来送你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因为今天是阳毬日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 是错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个海獭感觉跟真的一样 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是海獭的话 已经有小冠了就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里让他模仿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他还会模仿吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会模仿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是阳毬日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶呢 就模仿海马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要模仿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 今天我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王大人~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心得好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝带要什么颜色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…要粉色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里啊 我找了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老哥太慢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那阳毬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不好好看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到刚才我们都在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 谁叫下救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个女孩子在广场上晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注射一瓶肾上腺素 一单位阿托品…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.34,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}高仓小姐? 高仓阳毬小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠 小晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬…为什么这么突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个医生 看来也不一定就是庸医
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说能活下来才是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们做好随时可能会来的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有痛苦 而且还去了回忆中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说是幸福的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我们先联系池部叔叔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有各种各样的手续 我们也办不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然敢对自己的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的妹妹说出这么冷淡的话!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是接受了事实而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会是阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是一个 光和家人一起吃饭就会说幸福的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是对我们的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存 战略!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从通往你等命运之地而来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆幸吧 我决定把这女孩的余生再略微延长下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 想让这女孩一直保持复活状态…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…是哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 阳毬还活着!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 你哭了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大惊小怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 我到底是怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是医院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 得去告诉鹫塚医生一声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等我一下 我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:12:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开吃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的哎 这个煎鸡蛋好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次也教我做这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这点事什么时候都行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的味噌汤也很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后我也要一起分担家事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶一个人太辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你不过是打扫打扫浴室而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃这么多不要紧吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生也说能做的事就多做些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过几天能不能回学校呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:43.27,flashback_br,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(300,0)}东鸥医院 诊室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:40.89,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)}鹫塚医生很震惊。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:43.27,flashback_red,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}他目睹了自己从医经历中最为惊奇的一幕。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能从当时的状况恢复到现在这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且情况还很稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这简直可以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大清早的竟然有快递来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁寄来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄件信息也没写…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫「冷冻运输」的 难道这是生鲜食品?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是茄子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这么说 不觉得太大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还冻起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马 看时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 阳毬就拜托你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匆匆忙忙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 这玩意儿要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也塞不进冰箱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我原以为这不过是走运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为又不讲理又残酷的神明 出于一时高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便为我们的命运带来了奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是因为即使连我们这种人 也有幸福的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 高仓家弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝个下午茶不~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现了一个超可爱的女孩在那打工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我今天得赶紧回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太无情啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别趴上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个露肚脐的女孩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老哥的话一定会跟我去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我跟冠叶划等号!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樱花女高的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到没 中间那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:33.37,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不知道 男人嘛男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是相当…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.67,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那还是无视吧 无视掉无视掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦回过头来了 在看这里!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 莫非在看我?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上几年级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:42.38,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}呐 去喝下午茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.79,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好啊 去哪家?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边上那个短发的也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么觉得吧 高仓家弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 定期车票不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了 上体育课换衣服的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放更衣柜里了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企鹅?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的定期车票…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好贵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我冒昧地问一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这企鹅是什么情况?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 那个哥哥在说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 别多看 赶紧过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人还看不见…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 还是淋湿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件诡异的事情啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它带伞去了 没遇上吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「没遇上」?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 在那地方把线穿过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底…是啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么情况啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个快递解冻以后就是这群小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还听得懂我们说话 至少能帮忙跑个腿啥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不对! 这也太奇怪了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 这群家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 除我们以外的人都看不见它们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存战略!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知你等必将一事无成之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 啥? 啥?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要得到企鹅罐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.16,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(746,660)}Penguin Drum
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀 阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并非你等的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从你等的命运所至之地而来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帽子在操纵阳毬!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧… 那不是在水族馆买的玩具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩现因我的神力得以暂续生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而天下没有免费的午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要收下这条命的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 代价什么的不奇怪吗——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来进行生存战略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是为何而生的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若创造人类的目的 是只为让其度过忙碌一生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是一种惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一个讽刺的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若真是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠于基因内编写好的生存战略而生活的动物 反而更加简单和美好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这世上真有神明 我只想问他一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人世间 真的存在「命运」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬 不行啦 快点醒过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被操纵了啦 帽子把你整个人变掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人类无视命运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视本能和基因的命令 而爱上了某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 那他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能被称为人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 讨厌「命运」这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:54.63,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}1{\fs30\pos(640,630)}ST STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:54.63,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之钟鸣响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.00,0:00:-10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.66,0:23:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢「命运」这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何一件事是无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着命运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.41,0:23:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来进行生存战略吧
